cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the integration of finite model finding techniques into SMT solvers, which is a topic related to logic and automated reasoning (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of constraint solving techniques (cs.AI) and the on-demand instantiation of quantified formulas (cs.PL). The experiments conducted in the paper also involve the use of data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering techniques (cs.SE) to implement and evaluate the proposed approach.
